### enqueue
```java
// From ArrayBlockingQueue
// 入队并唤醒线程，需要先持有锁
private void enqueue(E x) {
    final Object[] items = this.items;
    items[putIndex] = x; // 入队
    if (++putIndex == items.length)
        putIndex = 0; // 重置putIndex
    count++;
    // 唤醒等待notEmpty的线程，需要先持有锁
    notEmpty.signal();
}
```

